Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Governor Doug Burgum: "We've never had a candidate like Harris, 56 days before the election, who's gone under so little scrutiny. We have one interview, no debates. This has never happened in modern politics...even when she finally puts policies on her website this week, it's already been revealed...that most of that was cut and pasted from the Biden website…”
